    <h1>Discrimination — Your Legal Protections</h1>
    <p class="lede">Federal and state laws protect you from discrimination based on race, national origin, religion, immigration status, and other characteristics. These protections apply broadly — at work, in housing, in public places, and at school.</p>
    <p class="updated">Updated as of April 30, 2026</p>
  </div>
</section>

